name: Möbius Portal #2
description:
The Möbius portal series is a collaboration between spogelsesmaskinen and @ itsgalo hicetnunc.xyz/itsgalo

Based on the Möbius transformation of a tesseract, the four-dimensional analogue of the cube.

Palms, IBM PS2, 8086, Möbius transformation, 320x240 scaled x 2, 8 Colors, 180 frames, spøgelsesmaskinen, itsgalo, 2021
